---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Fit 77 Training Center · Gimnasio en Kanasín, Yucatán"
  description="Coaches de primer nivel, un método que se siente y la calidad humana que hace que te quedes. ⭐ 4.6 con 23 reseñas en Google. Gimnasio en San Antonio Kaua III, Kanasín. Escríbenos por WhatsApp."
  slug="fit-77-training-center"
  ogImage="/fit-77-training-center/img/foto_2.jpg"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
  favicon="🏋️"
  themeColor="#0f1b2d"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/529992235843"}
  telefono={"999 223 5843"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=643663692156401951&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <main class="f77">

    <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <img class="hero-photo" src="/fit-77-training-center/img/foto_2.jpg" alt="Clase grupal entrenando en Fit 77 Training Center" />
      <div class="hero-scrim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="hero-track" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="wrap hero-content">
        <p class="kicker reveal">Gimnasio · San Antonio Kaua III, Kanasín</p>

        <h1 class="wordmark reveal">
          <span class="fit">FIT</span>
          <span class="bib">
            <span class="pin pin-tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="pin pin-tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="pin pin-bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="pin pin-br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="bib-num">77</span>
          </span>
          <span class="tc">Training Center</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="tagline reveal">Coaches de primer nivel, un método que se siente y la actitud para que no le falles a tus metas.</p>

        <a class="chip reveal" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=643663692156401951&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.6 · 23 reseñas en Google
        </a>

        <div class="cta-row reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://wa.me/529992235843" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2zm0 18.2c-1.5 0-3-.4-4.3-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1-.2.3-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-3.4-3c-.3-.4 0-.5.2-.7l.4-.5c.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5v-.5c0-.1-.5-1.3-.7-1.8-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.3.3-.9.9-.9 2.2s.9 2.5 1 2.7c.1.2 1.8 2.8 4.4 3.9.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.6.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2l-.4-.3z"/></svg>
            Escríbenos por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=643663692156401951&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.2 7 13 7 13s7-7.8 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7zm0 9.5A2.5 2.5 0 1 1 12 6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5z"/></svg>
            Cómo llegar
          </a>
        </div>

        <dl class="datos reveal">
          <div><dt>4.6 <span aria-hidden="true">★</span></dt><dd>calificación real en Google</dd></div>
          <div><dt>23</dt><dd>reseñas de socios</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Lun–Vie</dt><dd>7:00–9:00 y 17:00–21:00</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ============ 01 EL MÉTODO ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="metodo">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Lo que nos distingue</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">No es solo un gimnasio,<br />es un <span class="lima-text">training center</span></h2>

        <div class="pillars">
          <article class="pillar reveal">
            <span class="pillar-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
            <h3>Coaches de primer nivel</h3>
            <p>Instructores que corrigen tu técnica, ajustan tu rutina en el momento y no te sueltan a medio entrenamiento.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="pillar reveal">
            <span class="pillar-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
            <h3>Calidad humana primero</h3>
            <p>El trato es tan importante como el peso que levantas. Se nota desde el primer día — y es lo que más repiten en Google.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="pillar reveal">
            <span class="pillar-num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
            <h3>Metas, no solo sesiones</h3>
            <p>Venimos a ayudarte a llegar a donde te propusiste, con seguimiento real, no a rentarte una caminadora.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 02 QUIÉNES SOMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="nosotros">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Quiénes somos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Entrenamos contigo,<br />no solo te cronometramos</h2>
        <div class="about reveal">
          <p>Somos <strong>Fit 77 Training Center</strong>, un gimnasio en la Av. 77 de San Antonio Kaua III, en Kanasín. Desde el primer día trabajamos igual: técnica cuidada, seguimiento constante y coaches que entrenan a tu lado — no solo cronometrando desde un escritorio.</p>
          <p>Eso es justo lo que más se repite en nuestras reseñas de Google: el método, la calidad humana de los coaches y unas instalaciones que se sienten cuidadas. No es casualidad — es la forma en que trabajamos, con rutinas pensadas para tus metas y no genéricas.</p>
          <p>Si llevas tiempo posponiendo el gimnasio, o buscas un lugar donde de verdad te ayuden a llegar a tu meta, te esperamos de lunes a viernes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 03 INSTALACIONES ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="instalaciones">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Qué vas a encontrar</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Instalaciones para<br />entrenar en serio</h2>

        <div class="ofrece-grid">
          <ul class="ofrece reveal">
            <li>Zona de pesas libres y mancuernas</li>
            <li>Rack funcional con barras, argollas y bandas</li>
            <li>Kettlebells y equipo de peso libre</li>
            <li>Clases grupales dirigidas por coach</li>
            <li>Cardio funcional en circuito</li>
            <li>Coaching y seguimiento personalizado</li>
          </ul>
          <figure class="ofrece-foto reveal">
            <img src="/fit-77-training-center/img/foto_5.jpg" alt="Entrenamiento con barra en Fit 77 Training Center" loading="lazy" />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 04 RESEÑAS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="resenas">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Prueba social</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal"><span class="lima-text">4.6 de 5</span> en 23 reseñas</h2>
        <div class="reviews reveal">
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Excelente atención, método e instructores de primer nivel 👍🏽»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Manuel Garcia</strong><span>Hace 7 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Un buen lugar para entrenar, y sobre todo la calidad humana que tienen los couch, un lugar para lograr los desafíos que uno se propone»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Reina Isabel Bacab</strong><span>Hace un año · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Excelente la calidad de las instalaciones del gimnasio en sí, y sobre todo de las entrenadoras. Llevo medio mes y me siento bastante agusta.»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Safiro Segovia</strong><span>Hace 5 años · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <div class="center reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=643663692156401951&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 05 UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="eyebrow reveal">Dónde estamos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Av. 77, San Antonio<br />Kaua III, Kanasín</h2>
        <div class="ubica reveal">
          <div class="ubica-info">
            <p class="dir">Av 77 265-Por 60 y 62, San Antonio Kaua III<br />97370 Kanasín, Yucatán</p>
            <a class="btn btn-solid btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=643663692156401951&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en Google Maps</a>
            <h3 class="horario-titulo">Horario de entrenamiento</h3>
            <table class="horarios">
              <tbody>
                <tr data-dia="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>7:00–9:00, 17:00–21:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>7:00–9:00, 17:00–21:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>7:00–9:00, 17:00–21:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>7:00–9:00, 17:00–21:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>7:00–9:00, 17:00–21:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="mapa">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Fit%2077%20Training%20Center%2C%20Av%2077%20265-Por%2060%20y%2062%2C%20San%20Antonio%20Kaua%20III%2C%2097370%20Kanas%C3%ADn%2C%20Yuc.%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
              title="Mapa: Fit 77 Training Center en Kanasín, Yucatán"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="banda">
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="banda-title">¿Listo para empezar?</h2>
        <p class="banda-sub">Escríbenos y agenda tu primera sesión con nuestros coaches.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/529992235843" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp directo</a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark-ghost" href="tel:+529992235843">Llamar · 999 223 5843</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="pie">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="pie-logo">FIT<span class="lima-text">77</span></p>
        <p class="pie-dato">Training Center · Av 77 265-Por 60 y 62, San Antonio Kaua III, 97370 Kanasín, Yuc.</p>
        <p class="pie-dato"><a href="tel:+529992235843">999 223 5843</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/529992235843" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a> · <a href="https://www.facebook.com/share/17LTcU88S7/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a></p>
        <p class="pie-mini">Lunes a viernes 7:00–9:00 y 17:00–21:00 · Sábado y domingo cerrado</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HealthClub",
    "name": "Fit 77 Training Center",
    "telephone": "+529992235843",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/fit-77-training-center",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "Av 77 265-Por 60 y 62, San Antonio Kaua III",
      "addressLocality": "Kanasín",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97370",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.6",
      "reviewCount": "23"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Fr 07:00-09:00", "Mo-Fr 17:00-21:00"]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --navy: #0f1b2d;
      --navy-deep: #0a141f;
      --lima: #a3e635;
      --paper: #f4f7f2;
      --steel: #334155;
      --steel-light: #7e8fa6;
      --line: rgba(244, 247, 242, 0.14);
      --display: "Chakra Petch", "Arial Narrow", sans-serif;
      --body: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--paper);
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .f77 ::selection { background: var(--lima); color: var(--navy-deep); }
    .f77 a:focus-visible,
    .f77 .btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--lima);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .lima-text { color: var(--lima); }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 38px);
      min-height: calc(100svh - 38px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding: 48px 0 40px;
      overflow: hidden;
      isolation: isolate;
    }
    .hero-photo {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      z-index: -3;
      filter: grayscale(0.25) contrast(1.05);
    }
    .hero-scrim {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -2;
      background:
        linear-gradient(0deg, var(--navy) 6%, rgba(15, 27, 45, 0.78) 42%, rgba(15, 27, 45, 0.55) 68%, rgba(15, 27, 45, 0.35) 100%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 92% -6%, rgba(163, 230, 53, 0.16), transparent 60%);
    }
    .hero-track {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: -1;
      background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(244, 247, 242, 0.05) 0 2px, transparent 2px 64px);
    }

    .kicker {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--lima);
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }

    .wordmark {
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: baseline;
      column-gap: 0.18em;
      row-gap: 4px;
    }
    .wordmark .fit {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: clamp(44px, 13vw, 118px);
      line-height: 0.86;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      color: var(--paper);
    }
    .wordmark .bib {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      border: 3px solid var(--lima);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 0 0.14em;
      background: rgba(163, 230, 53, 0.07);
      transform: rotate(-3deg);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    }
    .wordmark .bib-num {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(56px, 17vw, 156px);
      line-height: 0.82;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      color: var(--lima);
    }
    .pin {
      position: absolute;
      width: 9px;
      height: 9px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--paper);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px var(--navy-deep);
    }
    .pin-tl { top: -5px; left: -5px; }
    .pin-tr { top: -5px; right: -5px; }
    .pin-bl { bottom: -5px; left: -5px; }
    .pin-br { bottom: -5px; right: -5px; }
    .wordmark .tc {
      flex-basis: 100%;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: clamp(15px, 3.4vw, 20px);
      letter-spacing: 0.32em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--steel-light);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(18px, 4.4vw, 23px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--paper);
      max-width: 36ch;
      margin: 22px 0 16px;
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--paper);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(244, 247, 242, 0.05);
    }
    .chip .star { color: var(--lima); }
    .chip:hover { border-color: var(--lima); }

    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin: 24px 0 0; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 17px;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--lima); color: var(--navy-deep); }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: #b9f24e; }
    .btn-ghost { border: 2px solid var(--line); color: var(--paper); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--lima); color: var(--lima); }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 15px; padding: 12px 18px; }

    .datos {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 40px 0 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 20px;
      max-width: 620px;
    }
    .datos dt {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(22px, 5.5vw, 32px);
      color: var(--paper);
    }
    .datos dt span { color: var(--lima); }
    .datos dd { margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--steel-light); line-height: 1.4; }

    /* ---------- SECCIONES ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 76px 0; }
    .sec-panel { background: var(--navy-deep); }
    .eyebrow {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--lima);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 7.4vw, 54px);
      line-height: 1.04;
      margin: 0 0 32px;
      color: var(--paper);
    }

    /* ---------- MÉTODO / PILARES ---------- */
    .pillars {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .pillar {
      padding: 22px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .pillar:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .pillar-num {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--lima);
      border: 2px solid var(--lima);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .pillar h3 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 21px;
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      color: var(--paper);
    }
    .pillar p { margin: 0; color: var(--steel-light); font-size: 15.5px; max-width: 44ch; }

    /* ---------- ABOUT ---------- */
    .about p { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 0 18px; color: #cdd6e3; }
    .about strong { color: var(--paper); }

    /* ---------- INSTALACIONES ---------- */
    .ofrece-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; align-items: start; }
    .ofrece {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .ofrece li {
      position: relative;
      padding: 14px 0 14px 26px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: #cdd6e3;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .ofrece li:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .ofrece li::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 22px;
      width: 10px;
      height: 3px;
      background: var(--lima);
    }
    .ofrece-foto img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      filter: grayscale(0.15) contrast(1.03);
    }

    /* ---------- RESEÑAS ---------- */
    .reviews {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
    }
    .rev {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--navy);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }
    .rev-stars {
      color: var(--lima);
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .rev blockquote {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--paper);
    }
    .rev figcaption {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .rev figcaption strong {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--paper);
    }
    .rev figcaption span { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--steel-light); }
    .center { text-align: center; }

    /* ---------- UBICACIÓN ---------- */
    .ubica { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .dir { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0 0 16px; color: #cdd6e3; }
    .horario-titulo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 19px;
      margin: 30px 0 10px;
      color: var(--paper);
    }
    .horarios { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 14.5px; }
    .horarios th, .horarios td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
    .horarios th { font-weight: 500; color: var(--paper); }
    .horarios td { color: var(--steel-light); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th, .horarios tr.hoy td { color: var(--navy-deep); background: var(--lima); font-weight: 600; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th::after {
      content: "hoy";
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--navy-deep);
      color: var(--lima);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-left: 10px;
      vertical-align: 1px;
    }
    .mapa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: block;
      filter: grayscale(0.3) contrast(1.02);
    }

    /* ---------- CTA FINAL ---------- */
    .banda {
      background: var(--lima);
      color: var(--navy-deep);
      padding: 64px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .banda-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(30px, 7vw, 48px);
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .banda-sub { margin: 0 auto 24px; max-width: 42ch; font-weight: 500; }
    .banda .cta-row { justify-content: center; }
    .btn-dark { background: var(--navy-deep); color: var(--paper); }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--navy); }
    .btn-dark-ghost { border: 2px solid rgba(10, 20, 31, 0.5); color: var(--navy-deep); }
    .btn-dark-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--navy-deep); }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .pie {
      padding: 44px 0 96px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--navy-deep);
    }
    .pie-logo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 26px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--paper);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .pie-dato { margin: 4px 0; color: var(--steel-light); font-size: 14px; }
    .pie-dato a { color: var(--paper); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--lima); }
    .pie-dato a:hover { color: var(--lima); }
    .pie-mini { margin: 14px 0 0; color: var(--steel); font-size: 12px; }

    /* ---------- REVEAL (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- DESKTOP ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .sec { padding: 108px 0; }
      .pillars { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); column-gap: 32px; }
      .pillar:nth-child(2), .pillar:nth-child(3) { border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .pillar:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
      .ofrece-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); align-items: start; }
      .ubica { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; align-items: start; }
      .mapa iframe { height: 400px; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var d = document;
      d.documentElement.classList.add('js');

      // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
      var hoy = new Date().getDay(); // 0 = domingo
      var fila = d.querySelector('.horarios tr[data-dia="' + hoy + '"]');
      if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

      // Scroll-reveal (mejora progresiva)
      var els = d.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        els.forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      } else {
        els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
